entries.s_12: Do you know a woman named Narlissa?
entries.s_14: Yes. I know her. I think they moved her down to the detention cells.
entries.s_18: I don't know. You'll have to check the security computer for that.
entries.s_20: Hey, I don't want any trouble with you. I haven't hurt anyone. In fact, I am on my way out and never coming back.
entries.s_5: Working here was a mistake. A terrible mistake.
entries.s_7: Why are you just now starting to realize that?
entries.s_9: They want me to bring some more people down to the detention cells. They torture and kill people down there. I can't hurt these people. I even know some of them. I need to get out of here.
